cs.DB, cs.CL, cs.LO, cs.DS, cs.FL 

This paper is primarily focused on Information Extraction (IE) from text documents, which is a subfield of both databases (cs.DB) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of regular expressions and relational algebra also suggests a connection to formal language theory (cs.FL) and logic (cs.LO). Finally, the paper's focus on the expressive power of recursive Datalog suggests a connection to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
